        <div class=" md:mt-32 mt-16 mb-10">
          <h2 class=" text-white mb-2">Alim Funeral Services</h2>
          <p class="text-white text-opacity-75  mt-8">Life, as we know it, is a fleeting journey, and death is a departure that every soul must experience. We're here to assure you that this departure is respected, honored, and performed according to the sacred rituals of Islam.</p>
        </div>
      </div>  
      <div class="md:col-span-4">

      </div>     
    </div>
    <div class="grid  md:grid-cols-12 gap-0 md:gap-10 bg-hero-img-funeral p-8 ">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
      <a href="#" class="button-style  block w-full text-center p-4 mt-28" > Learn more </a>
      </div> 
      <div class="md:col-span-10">
      <p class="text-white text-opacity-75 mt-5 md:mt-28">Our platform allows mosque, funeral home, and cemetery to work collaboratively and provide a complete set of Muslim funeral services for your loved ones.</p>
      </div>    
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="living-better-life-section bg-mountain-bg lg:pb-450  md:pb-96 pb-44">
    
    <div class="container  max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4">
      
    
      
